title: Beautiful Two Bedroom One Bath Home  Near Snowden Elementary
posting_body: Beautiful two-bedroom one-bath home located within the EverGreen community of Memphis, Tn.
Gorgeous kitchen and bath and spacious laundry room/pantry.
The home has been fully renovated throughout and includes central heat and air.
Three minutes from the Zoo and Snowden Elementary school, Four minutes from the Square of Midtown on Madison and 10 minutes from Downtown Memphis.
